      "releaseNotes": "• Tempo Advance now runs natively on iOS 13\n• Fixed setlist and theme files import option missing from Mail app on iOS 13\n• Fixed engine stall on returning to Tempo while earphones are in use, on older devices running iOS 13\n• Other minor bug fixes",
